welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Laplace, where the charm of our small town will capture your heart! Known for its southern hospitality and delicious Cajun cuisine, we invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

airports.airport_name: Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is a domestic terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport, serving airlines such as American, Delta, and United.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is a domestic terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport, serving airlines such as Southwest and JetBlue.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is an international terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport, serving airlines such as Air Canada, British Airways, and Lufthansa.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport and is free to use.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lakefront Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lakefront Airport caters to private and corporate flights.
